<li><a href="/wiki/Elaine_massacre" title="Elaine massacre">Elaine massacre</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Red_Summer" title="Red Summer">Red Summer</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Chicago_race_riot_of_1919" title="Chicago race riot of 1919">Chicago race riot of 1919</a></li>
